Guangdong exports 3.76 billion us dollars of high - tech products in first two months of this year
Xinhua news agency , Guangzhou , march 16 ( reporter Chen ji ) - the latest statistics show that from january to february this year , Guangdong province exported 3.76 billion us dollars of high and new technology products , up 34.8 percent over the same period last year , accounting for 25.5% of the province 's total export value .
the export of high and new technology products has seen frequent bright spots , which have made important contributions to the growth of Guangdong 's foreign trade .
last year , Guangdong province exported 22,294 million us dollars of new and high - tech products , up 31 percent over the same period of last year , 27.2 percentage points higher than the province 's export growth rate . the net increase in exports of new and high - tech products was 5.27 billion us dollars , making up for the decline in the export value of traditional labor - intensive products brought about by falling prices .
among Guangdong 's exports of new and high - tech products , computer and telecommunications technology products outshone all the others , with a total export value of $ 19.14 billion last year , accounting for 85.9 percent of the province 's total export value of new and high - tech products .
the main markets for the export of new and high technology products from Guangdong Province are Hong Kong , the United States , the European Union and Japan .
last year , the total export volume of the high and new technology industrial belt in the pearl river delta reached $ 21.99 billion , accounting for 98.7% of the province 's total export volume of high and new technology products .
this year , this dominant role is still very conspicuous .
at present , over 95% of the computers in the pearl river delta region are fully equipped to provide all computer spare parts except CPU .
FIFA to punish cheating in football field
Xinhua news agency , beijing , march 17 , the executive committee of the international football federation ( FIFA ) revealed on the 16 th that in this year 's world cup , the referees will adopt stricter measures to deal with those players who profit by diving and other means .
according to foreign reports , the FIFA executive committee said in a press release that it would fully support the referees in strictly enforcing the law , especially against players who deceive the spectators .
the FIFA Executive Committee also announced a number of reform measures .
FIFA rules that no words should be written on players ' waistcoats starting july 1 this year , and that FIFA allows advertisements to appear on players ' uniforms but only in front of them , as long as the players write contradictory words on their waistcoats .
suicide bombings in jerusalem
Xinhua news agency report of march 17 from jerusalem ( by staff reporter Zhong cuihua and nie xiaoyang ) - a man detonated an accompanying bomb next to a bus in a residential area in northern jerusalem on the afternoon of the 17th . the perpetrators were killed on the spot and nine others were slightly injured . they were taken to hospital for medical treatment .
at present , the police have sealed off the explosion site .
less than two hours ago , there was a palestinian shooting incident in the northern Israeli town of Kafsa Sabah .
according to the latest reports , a 16 - year - old Israeli girl was killed and at least 12 others were wounded .
the gunman was shot dead by the police .
at present , no organization has claimed responsibility for the attack .
the Israeli Prime Minister &apos;s Office condemned the shooting .
Israeli prime minister Sharon said on the same day that although Israel and the palestinian side are currently engaged in cease-fire efforts , Israel will react to any attack .
civil service painting and calligraphy competition to mark 5 th anniversary of Hong kong 's return to the motherland
Xinhua news agency , Hangzhou , march 18 , this year marks the fifth anniversary of Hong kong 's return to the motherland and marks the promulgation and implementation of china 's first " code of conduct for state functionaries . " to celebrate these two happy events , a calligraphy and painting competition for state functionaries will be launched among Hong kong , Macao , and mainland government functionaries with the creation of the theme of the public servants of the state functionaries in lien tan .
the competition was organised by the Hong Kong Wen Po , the China Mayors Association and the Hong Kong Cultural and Leisure Services Department .
the public servants participating in the competition will create and express the scenery of the motherland in the form of chinese paintings and write poems , poems , songs , and oeuvres . they will also create calligraphy works based on the norms of conduct , wise words , mottos , and aphorisms jointly observed by public servants . they will advocate the style of honesty , diligence , pragmatism , and conscientiousness in performing official duties , so as to enhance the cultural accomplishment and professional level of public servants .
the competition will highlight the festive atmosphere of the fifth anniversary of Hong kong 's return to the motherland and fully display the artistic charm of chinese painting and calligraphy .
it is learned that the deadline for the collection of works for the competition will be april 20 , 2002 .
the winning entries will be collected for publication and distribution on the fifth anniversary of Hong kong 's reunification .
ANC opposes sanctions against Zimbabwe
Xinhua news agency , Johannesburg , march 18 ( reporter plateau ) general secretary of south africa 's ruling african national congress ( ANC ) Motland criticized the united states , britain , and other western countries here on the 18th in an attempt to force Zimbabwe to act according to the wishes of western countries through sanctions .
in response to the threat of sanctions against Zimbabwe threatened by western countries , Motland told the press : " it is up to the Zimbabwean people to decide who should lead Zimbabwe . it is not up to the western countries to decide who should lead Zimbabwe . "
he pointed out : mutual respect for state sovereignty is an international norm that every country must abide by . the ANC resolutely opposes sanctions imposed by western countries against a sovereign country .
Motlanthe said that if western countries impose further sanctions on Zimbabwe , not only will this not help , but it will also aggravate the unrest in Zimbabwean society .
he called on the Zimbabwean government and opposition parties to work together to overcome the food shortage and land crisis .
he stressed that only by strengthening unity can any attempt to split Zimbabwe be thwarted .
earlier , the ANC issued a statement demanding that the international community respect the choices of the Zimbabwean people and help them tide over difficulties .
Zimbabwean president Robert Mugabe was re - elected in the march 9 - 11 presidential election , but western countries accused the election of serious fraud and lack of fairness and freedom , so they refused to acknowledge the election results and threatened to impose further sanctions on Zimbabwe .
at present , some western countries have announced the termination of economic aid to Zimbabwe .
before the election , eu countries had imposed targeted sanctions on Zimbabwe on the grounds that the government had restricted press freedom and obstructed supervision .
French athletes return to Paris for paralympic winter olympics
Xinhua news agency , Paris , march 18 ( reporter wang Jingcheng ) french athletes who participated in the paralympic winter olympics held in salt lake city , united states from march 7 to 16 returned to Paris today .
at the de Gaulle airport , the athletes were warmly welcomed by the french minister of youth and sports , Bifei , the representative of the minister responsible for family , children , and handicapped people , Sejong Royale , and others concerned .
the french team , which participated in the eighth paralympic winter games in salt lake city , the united states , won a total of 19 medals at the games , of which nine were won by women athletes , including one gold medal and 10 by men athletes , including one gold medal .
this was the best performance of the French delegation at the Winter Olympics .
speaking at the welcoming ceremony , Sejon Royale said that the french athletes have changed society 's view of them with their special performance , and the french people are grateful for their outstanding contributions in the struggle to change people 's view of the disabled .
the french government will , as always , continue to support sports for the disabled , the minister said in his speech .
Jordan returns from injury as early as Sunday
Xinhua news agency , washington , march 19 ( reporter Xie Peilin ) - after undergoing surgery on his right knee , jin feiren and Jordan are expected to recover as early as Sunday . however , as the regular season is drawing to a close , it seems difficult for the washington wizards to hit the playoffs because of this .
Wizards coach Collins revealed today that Jordan has stepped up his rehabilitation efforts . although he does not want to make appearances in Denver and salt lake city on Wednesday and Thursday , he is likely to go to Toronto on Sunday to put on the Wizards clothes again to challenge the raptors , who are currently in poor condition .
Collins said : " he may appear at any time . it all depends on how he feels . "
at present , the focus of his training is on defense , while also practicing shooting .
he is prepared to increase his strength slightly to see if his body can adapt .
as far as the knee is concerned , he said it was at least 100 percent better than before the operation .
Jordan scored an average of 24 points this season . he underwent surgery three weeks ago . during this period , the team won four games and lost eight .
at present , there are only 15 games left in the regular season , with the Wizards 31-36 , ranking 10th in the eastern league , behind the Miami heatwaves by half , and leading the raptors by one game , but still two and a half games away from the eighth place - winning Charlotte Hornets .
coach Collins naturally hopes that Jordan 's comeback will enable the team to make a qualitative leap forward , at least to win successively in a short period of time , thus reviving the hope of the playoffs .
Collins said : " if Jordan had not been absent due to injury , we would have won at least three more games earlier . "
as far as the current situation is concerned , he is fully capable of activating the team in time .
South Korea will send a message to North Korea that it hopes to resume talks
Xinhua news agency , Seoul , march 19 ( reporter Zhang li ) - according to a report by Yonhap news agency , the south Korean government has submitted a request to Indonesian president Megawati to convey to north Korean leader Kim Chong - il south Korean president Kim tae - Chung 's message that south Korean president Kim tae - Chung hopes to resume talks between north and south korea and between north korea and the united states as soon as possible .
an official of the ROK government said : the contents of the information include that the ROK , the united states , and japan all hope to resolve the issue through dialogue with the DPRK , and hope that the DPRK side will adopt a positive attitude .
it is reported that Indonesian president Megawati will visit the DPRK from 28 to 30 march and the ROK from 30 march to 1 april .
the ROK government has already conveyed this message to the Indonesian side through diplomatic channels .
the ROK government denied a report in japan 's Asahi Shimbun that Megawati would hand over Kim tae - Chung 's handwritten letter to Kim Chong - il .
European Central Bank Officials Say Eurozone Economy to Speed Up within Year
Xinhua news agency report of march 20 from Brussels ( by staff reporter wang xingqiao ) - european central bank chief economist Dr. Issing said here on the 20th that the euro zone economy has come out of its doldrums and will begin to pick up faster this year .
Issing made the above remarks at a hearing held by the european parliament in Brussels .
he said the latest data showed that the euro zone economy had picked up slowly at the beginning of this year , and the rate of economic recovery was expected to accelerate within the year .
the euro zone is expected to grow at a rate of 2 to 2.5 percent this year .
Issing believes that the rebound of the euro zone 's economy is mainly due to the growth of consumer spending and the fact that commodity inventories in the euro zone are now approaching very low levels .
with regard to inflation , Issing said that the inflation rate in the euro zone as a whole has shown a downward trend , and there is no indication that there will be a risk of price instability in the middle stage of economic development .
commenting on the current world energy situation , Issin said that the recent rise in world oil market prices has aroused the concern of economic policy makers in various countries , and the impact of the oil price rise on the long - term economic trend should not be underestimated .
Hong kong police first detected trafficking in dangerous drugs on internet
Xinhua news agency , Hong kong , march 21 ,
the narcotics bureau of the Hong kong police force pointed out that this was the first discovery made by the Hong kong police and should be taken seriously .
the Hong kong police said that in the past year , a total of several cases of Hong kong people using the internet to pay by credit card to purchase ecstasy and other drugs had been detected .
drug traffickers buy drugs in Thailand and mail them to drug users in Hong kong .
the chief superintendent of the narcotics bureau of the Hong kong police force , mr ip Lau - Chuen , pointed out that credit cards had been used for online ordering in a number of cases detected last year .
the Hong kong police are working with the relevant disciplined services to crack down on this new crime .
speaking at a seminar on cross - boundary organized crime held in Hong kong not long ago , the head of the un international narcotics commission pointed out that internet drug trafficking will be a new challenge for law enforcement agencies in the future .
the security bureau of the Hong kong special administrative region ( HKSAR ) completed the consultation on computer - related crimes last year and will amend the law to crack down on any use of computers to commit crimes .
African university students urge africa not to become a periphery of new technologies
Xinhua news agency , Abidjan , march 21 ( reporter song nan ) at the second forum of african institutions of higher learning , which opened on the 21st , university students attending the forum called on african youth to actively use high technology in the field of information and communications to meet the challenges of economic globalization and not to let the african continent become a remote region in the field of new technology .
in his speech , the chairman of the meeting held that new and high technologies have promoted the development of Asian , european , and american countries .
the arrival of the new century has brought many opportunities and challenges to the african continent . African young people should strive to master new and high technologies and make their own contributions to a better future for africa .
the theme of this year 's forum of african institutions of higher learning is : new technologies , information , and exchanges will bring more opportunities to african talent training .
during the three - day conference , experts from more than a dozen african universities and enterprises will discuss topics such as the future of africa and the challenges of new technologies , cultural diversity and economic development in tajikistan , and the opportunities and prospects that tajikistan 's e - commerce will bring to africa .
large @-@ scale campus cultural exhibitions will also be held during the conference .
Indonesia reiterates opposition to foreign military presence
Xinhua news agency , Jakarta , march 22 ( reporter mai tangyuan ) indonesia 's foreign ministry issued a press release on the 22nd reiterating its opposition to the stationing of foreign troops on the island .
the Indonesian foreign ministry reiterated this position in response to a report in the usa today newspaper on 20 march that the united states intends to send troops to indonesia to help crack down on members of the Asahi group who fled afghanistan .
according to the communique , the us government has never formally made such a request to the Indonesian government , which can also be confirmed by the us white house and defense department later denying the report .
the communique reiterated that indonesia pursues a positive and independent foreign policy , that indonesia has conducted close and beneficial cooperation with the united states and other countries to jointly oppose terrorism , and that the Indonesian government is willing to continue to strengthen cooperation in this regard .
Ukraine condemns us interference in its internal affairs
Xinhua news agency , Kiev , march 22 ( reporter Zhang Zhiqiang ) Ukrainian president Kuchma issued a statement to the press on the 22nd on the interference of the us house of representatives in ukraine 's internal affairs , saying that the us house resolution is an unprecedented event and that it is confusing and puzzling .
the us house of representatives on the 20th passed a resolution on the upcoming parliamentary elections in ukraine , calling on ukraine to guarantee transparent , free , and fair elections on the 31st of this month .
the resolution also pointed out : the Ukrainian government should earnestly implement the new parliamentary election law , and the election results should indicate whether ukraine will continue to carry out democratic reforms .
Kuchma said that the ethnic group of ukraine is not a football that can be manipulated at will , and Ukrainians should have their own dignity .
Kuchma also thanked Lozinski , president of the world congress of Ukrainians , for his letter to the us congress .
Lozinski said in his letter , " look at what you have done yourself . "
learn at home first , and then teach others .
Ukrainian communist party leader Simon Nienko said on the same day that the us act is a gross interference in ukraine 's internal affairs and a threat to ukraine 's national independence .
Zinchenko , leader of the united social democratic party of ukraine , said : a one - sided appraisal of ukraine 's election campaign in the us house of representatives resolution will lead to polarization of ukraine 's political forces .
a spokesman for the Ukrainian foreign ministry said today that the election of representatives of the supreme and local legislative organs of ukraine is purely a matter for the Ukrainian people .
in the final stage of the Ukrainian parliamentary election campaign , it is hoped that all countries will show caution and abide by the norms of international law , such as non - interference in internal affairs .
Arab countries unanimously oppose us attack on iraq
Xinhua news agency , Riyadh , march 23 , according to a report in the Riyadh newspaper on the 23rd , Lebanese president Lahoud said in an interview with the newspaper that although the arab summit has not yet opened , they have taken a unanimous stand on the iraq issue and opposed the united states ' attack on iraq .
Lahoud pointed out : no arab country agrees that the united states or its allies should attack any arab country without proper reasons . the united states must understand the consequences of such attacks , no matter what the pretexts or pretexts for attacks are .
Lahoud believes that the fight against terrorism or the axis of evil is an attractive pretext for influencing western public opinion , but criminal activities should not be carried out under such a pretext .
he also urged the united states not to adopt double standards , that is , to fight terrorism in one region while ignoring Israeli state terrorism in another region .
senior ROK officials to visit DPRK in april
Xinhua news agency , beijing , march 25 , according to information received here , a spokesman for the presidential office of the republic of korea announced in Seoul on the 25 th that ROK president Kim tae - Chung 's special adviser on foreign affairs , security , and reunification will visit the DPRK in the first week of april . he will hold talks with DPRK officials on the exchange of visits between separated relatives of the south and the north and on ways to ease tensions between the south and the north of the Korean peninsula .
the spokesman said : the DPRK side hopes that the talks will lay a foundation for resuming north - south relations , but she did not mention the details of the talks .
she said that details of the talks will be announced after Lin Dongyuan returns from north korea .
meanwhile , the DPRK central news agency also issued a brief statement on the same day , saying that president Kim tae - Chung 's special envoy will visit the DPRK .
the statement said that the two sides will hold talks on the serious situation on the Korean peninsula and issues of common concern .
Indonesian parliament speaker to stand trial
Xinhua news agency , beijing , march 25 , Indonesian parliament speaker Akbar Tandjung appeared in a Jakarta court on march 25 on charges of corruption and atonement , according to sources here .
Tanjung was accused of being responsible for the illegal diversion of 3.8 million us dollars of relief funds from indonesia 's state grain administration .
according to reports , the funds were later used to fund the 1999 election campaign of the professional bloc party led by Tandjung .
the relief funds were originally intended for poor families hit by the financial crisis , but investigators of the case found that the funds did not reach these families .
however , Tanjung has denied the above allegations .
analysts believe that regardless of the outcome of this trial , this incident may weaken Tanjung 's hope of being elected Indonesian president .
Tae Endeavour was delayed to launch due to a mechanical malfunction .
Xinhua news agency , washington , march 25 , due to technical problems with canada - made robots in the international space station , the launch of the space shuttle Asahi Endeavour will be postponed from may 6 to may 31 , the national aeronautics and space administration ( NASA ) said today .
it is reported that at that time , tan Endeavin will carry seven astronauts to the international space station for an 11 - day space flight .
the seven included astronauts from France and Russia .
a spokesman for the national aeronautics and space administration of the united states said that the space station staff can use this sufficient time to troubleshoot the malfunction , but the delay in launching also means that they will have to patiently stay for another three weeks , waiting for the united states ' Peggy Matson and two other russian astronauts to replace them .
Philip Zenperi from france is the first non - russian european astronaut to fly to the space station . he will carry out two space walks at the beginning of the mission .
shell 's total investment in china will reach 5 billion us dollars in three years
Xinhua news agency , beijing , march 26 ( reporter Qian chunxian ) shell group chairman wu zipei said a few days ago that shell group 's total investment in china will reach 5 billion us dollars by 2005 .
at the china development forum held here , he said that shell 's investment in china has already reached 1.6 billion us dollars , and with the addition of some projects being planned , the total investment in 2005 will reach 5 billion us dollars .
according to reports , shell is currently in talks with the chinese side on a number of cooperative projects .
among them , a joint venture project with Sinopec to establish 500 gas stations in Jiangsu is expected to start this year .
Mr ng said shell had been doing business with china for more than 100 years .
as far as shell is concerned , china 's market has great potential and is an important part of its global strategy .
with economic development , china 's energy demand is expected to double by 2020 , when china 's energy consumption will account for 16% of the world 's total .
China is facing severe energy challenges , and diversification of energy sources is very important to energy security and environmental protection . shell will play an important role in this process .
Xinhua news agency report of march 26th from the united nations ( by staff reporter gu zhenqiu ) - a un spokesman announced on the 26th that a un security council delegation will visit congo and other african countries involved in the congo conflict on april 27th to inject new vitality into the congo peace process .
the delegation , headed by french permanent representative to the united nations Levitte , will be composed of representatives of 15 un security council members , the spokesman said .
the main purpose of the visit is to conduct dialogue with the leaders of various parties to the conflict in the democratic republic of the congo ( DRC ) in order to urge the parties to the conflict to abide by the peace agreement they signed in the Zambian capital of Lusaka in 1999 .
this is the third time since may 2000 that the security council has sent a delegation to visit the great lakes region of africa .
Sri Lankan government to hold peace talks with LTTE
Xinhua news agency , Colombo , march 27 ( reporter Zhang Yadong ) the Sri Lankan government announced on the 27th that it plans to hold peace talks with the anti - government liberation tigers of Tamil Eelam in early may in an attempt to end nearly 20 years of bloody ethnic conflicts in the country .
Sri Lankan minister of justice , constitution , ethnic affairs and national integration Peris said at a press conference held on the same day that the Sri Lankan government and the tigers have agreed to hold peace talks as soon as possible , and the government hopes that the talks will be held in the first week of may .
he said : the initial talks will mainly prepare for entering into substantive talks .
the Sri Lankan government has not officially announced the venue of the talks , but there are reports that peace talks between the two sides will be held in Thailand .
Peris said that the government intends to hold talks with the tigers in a certain Asian country and has made relevant preparations for this .
in addition , it is reported that Barasimham , chief negotiator of the LTTE , who has been in exile in london for three years and returned to the LTTE - controlled areas in northern slovakia on the 25th , and Prabakaran , leader of the LTTE , recently held talks with Norwegian special envoy Solheim and Norwegian ambassador to slovakia in northern slovakia .
after the talks , the LTTE agreed to resume peace talks with the government when the situation in the areas under their control returned to normal , but still insisted that the government lift the ban on them before the peace talks .
in february this year , the Sri Lankan government and the tigers signed a permanent cease - fire agreement , laying a foundation for the two sides to start talks .
China Unicom 's net profit up nearly 38 percent last year
Xinhua news agency report of march 27th from Hong kong ( by staff reporter li Kai ) - china Unicom , a Hong kong - listed company , announced here today that china Unicom achieved good results in all fields of business in 2001 , with a total turnover of 29,393.3 billion yuan and a net profit of 4.457 billion yuan , an increase of nearly 38% over the previous year .
as one of china 's comprehensive telecommunications operators , china Unicom provides a variety of telecommunications services , including mobile communications , international and domestic long - distance calls , data , the internet , and paging .
China Unicom announced that last year , the company 's circuit - switched long - distance telephone and IP telephone business went to call and had a total time of 6.41 billion minutes , 5.9 times higher than that of the previous year , and its market share increased from 1.3 percent in 2000 to 7.7 percent , and the total time for connecting international calls increased 3.4 times over that of the previous year .
Yang Xianzu , CEO of China Unicom , said that this year , the company will continue to accelerate the development of mobile communications services , adopt a differentiated strategy , ensure the coordinated development of CDMA and GSM mobile communications services , and enable the company 's mobile phone users to continue to grow considerably .
China , japan sign currency swap agreement
Xinhua news agency , Tokyo , march 28 ( reporter wang Yan ) - dai xianglong , governor of the people 's bank of china , and Hayami , governor of the bank of japan , signed an agreement on bilateral currency exchange between the renminbi and the Japanese yen in Tokyo on the 28th .
according to the agreement , the people 's bank of china and the bank of japan can provide each other with a currency swap arrangement worth 3 billion us dollars if necessary to help them maintain the stability of the financial market .
the signing of a currency swap agreement between china and japan shows that cooperation between the central banks of the two countries has been further strengthened .
the agreement , signed by china and japan , is the second bilateral currency swap agreement signed between the people 's bank of china and the bank of Thailand in december 2001 .
in the future , china will also sign currency exchange agreements with south korea and some other countries .
Dai xianglong said : China will actively participate in asia 's financial cooperation , and is willing to make its own contribution to regional economic and financial stability and the prevention of risks together with other Asian countries and regions .
Wu Dawei , chinese ambassador to japan , attended the signing ceremony of the currency exchange agreement between the people 's bank of china and the bank of japan .
Afghanistan earthquake victims begin rebuilding homes
Xinhua news agency report of march 28 from Kabul ( by staff reporter pan yunzhao ) - three days after the earthquake , earthquake victims in the northern afghan province of Bagram have begun rebuilding their homes .
Rebecca , spokesman for the un office for the coordination of humanitarian assistance in afghanistan , told Xinhua that a central group composed of afghanistan 's interim government , un agencies , and non - governmental organizations ( ngos ) discovered on the 28th that the victims of the earthquake were already engaged in rebuilding their houses , and some of them also used relief materials provided by relief agencies to the victims .
she said that in view of this situation , un relief agencies have begun to consider the issue of helping disaster victims rebuild their homes .
at present , relief organizations already have a large amount of relief materials in stock in the earthquake - stricken areas and are distributing them to the victims through two methods : ground and air .
Afghanistan 's Nahrin and Berga regions were hit by a strong earthquake on friday , causing heavy casualties and leaving tens of thousands homeless .
Japan temporarily freezes humanitarian aid to russia
Xinhua news agency , Tokyo , march 29 , Japanese foreign minister Yoriko Kawaguchi announced on the 29 th that japan will temporarily freeze humanitarian aid to russia until the Japanese side carries out rectification and reform of the international committee in charge of aid projects .
Yoriko Kawaguchi said that in addition to maintaining the commission 's human expenditure and a technical cooperation project that japan is currently assisting russia , the Japanese government will control the financial assistance provided to russia through the commission until it is rectified .
the move was made in response to remarks made recently by Japanese finance minister Masajuro Ishikawa .
Yoshikawa Masajuro recently told cabinet members that in view of the continued deterioration of japan 's domestic finances , cabinet members should ensure that every sum of government funds can be used in a down - to - earth manner .
it has been learned that the committee has been accused of dereliction of duty and lack of transparency on the issue of where the funds are going after it was exposed that Suzuki tsuno , deputy chief cabinet secretary , unjustly pressured the foreign ministry and affected the procedures for applying for russian aid projects .
EU to hold consultations with china on implementation of temporary safeguard measures for steel imports
Xinhua news agency , beijing , march 29 ( reporter che yuming ) - shi Guangsheng , minister of foreign trade and economic cooperation , said here today that the eu has made a clear response to china 's concern that the eu will implement temporary safeguard measures on some imported steel products , saying that it will hold consultations with the chinese side as soon as possible and that china , as a developing country , will make some special arrangements to properly resolve this issue .
Shi Guangsheng answered a reporter 's question at a national conference on foreign economic and trade law today .
he said : at present , the iron and steel trade war is getting fiercer and fiercer , and the root cause is the united states .
at present , all parties concerned are making accusations and demands for bilateral consultations on the united states ' tong201 steel case , and some have even proposed to settle the case through the wto dispute settlement mechanism .
on 27 march , after the eu decided to impose temporary safeguard measures on 15 imported steel products from various countries , the chinese side made a prompt response . Shi Guangsheng immediately wrote to eu trade commissioner Lamy expressing his deep concern over this and offered to hold bilateral consultations with the eu .
train , car crash kills 7 in Liaoning
Xinhua news agency , Shenyang , march 30 ( reporter wang jun ) - at 1413 on march 29 , a train and car collided in Jinzhou city , Liaoning province , killing seven people and seriously injuring three others .
according to the safety inspection room of the Shenyang railway bureau , a four - wheel agricultural vehicle collided with a train from Jinzhou to Chengde when it seized a railway crossing between Lijiagou and zhou jiatun in yi county , Jinzhou city .
at that time , in addition to carrying 50 bags of fertilizer and seeds , the car also carried 14 people in violation of regulations .
at the time of the collision , four people jumped out of the car and escaped with no injuries . the other 10 were either killed or injured . the railway stop at the crossing was damaged and the locomotive of the train was also damaged to a certain extent .
after the accident , leaders of the ministry of railways , Shenyang railway bureau , Jinzhou city , and the local government rushed to the scene to deal with the aftermath .
the council of the arab states held an emergency meeting at the arab league headquarters on the same day to discuss the palestinian situation .
the meeting was attended by permanent representatives of 22 Arab States to the League .
speaking at a press conference after the meeting , Moussa said the escalation of Israeli military actions against palestine clearly shows Israel 's rejection of peace .
what is happening now is a continuation of Israel &apos;s military occupation of Palestine , and the Palestinian people will continue to resist Israeli aggression .
he said : as long as Israel 's military occupation of the palestinian territory exists for one day , and as long as Israeli tanks and soldiers exist in the palestinian territory for one day , the palestinian people 's resistance will continue for one day .
Xinhua news agency , jerusalem , march 31 ( reporter Zhong cuihua , nie xiaoyang ) - Israel 's security cabinet decided on the evening of the 31st to step up military strikes in palestinian - controlled areas and implement a series of planned military actions ahead of schedule .
on the afternoon of the same day , Israeli prime minister Sharon convened core ministers to hold consultations on the current Israeli - palestinian situation and how to deal with the increasingly frequent bombings by the palestinian side . the meeting decided to step up military strikes against the palestinian side .
according to political figures here , the security cabinet believes that intensifying attacks on the palestinian side will weaken the momentum of palestinian terrorist activities , but it will not be possible to stop such attacks once and for all .
Sharon will deliver a televised speech to the whole country at 0830 local time on the evening of the 31st ( 0130 local time on 1 april beijing time ) to explain to the public the government 's stance on handling the Israeli - palestinian conflict .
Cambodia , Vietnam hold trade fair
Xinhua news agency , Phnom Penh , april 1 ( reporter Yan ming ) - a joint Cambodian - Vietnamese commodities fair opened here on the 1 st , showcasing nearly 200 kinds of commodities .
a total of 50 businesses from cambodia and Vietnam participated in the exhibition , and 55 booths were set up .
exhibits include motorcycles , household appliances , agricultural tools , medicines , beverages , food , garments and so on .
Vietnamese ambassador to cambodia Nguyen dai Hong said at the opening ceremony that Vietnam and cambodia have great potential in economic and trade development , and that the holding of commodity fairs can further promote economic and trade cooperation and exchanges between the two countries .
he said : in recent years , the volume of trade between the two countries has made gratifying progress , increasing from $ 16.9 billion in 2000 to $ 1.8 billion in 2001 .
Cambodian commerce minister Champasseh said : it is a great thing for cambodia and Vietnam to jointly develop the two countries ' economy and trade . it is conducive to promoting the two countries ' economy and trade as well as the economic development of ASEAN countries . it will enable cambodia and Vietnam to integrate economically into ASEAN and the world economy at an early date .
Indonesian badminton expert thinks Taoufik &apos;s ranking is very favorable
Xinhua news agency , Jakarta , april 1 ( reporter mai tangyuan ) - ali Santo , chairman of the ancient Turkistan badminton club in central java , told antara news agency reporters in the provincial capital samborong on the 1st that the men 's singles player taoufik 's world ranking is very favorable to indonesia 's defending the Thomas cup .
he said that taoufik is now in the 33rd place , so that he can become a second or third singles player , which is less burdensome than the first singles player .
in group matches , a victory in the first singles event can affect subsequent matches , at least psychologically , affecting teammates and prompting them to strive to win .
however , if indonesia loses in the first singles , taoufik , as the second or third singles player , will hopefully score points , and the final victory or defeat will be decided by two doubles matches .
he believed that the possibility of indonesia defending the Thomas cup has increased with the return of taoufik , because the young player is a strong player in the world .
he believed that taoufik 's return would give indonesia hope to defeat its rivals , including host china .
according to the report , in a survey conducted by the badminton website , 45% of the people think that indonesia will be able to defend the Thomas cup , 21% think that china has a chance to win the championship , and 17% think that malaysia is a good team .
