this distance is the same as the distance that the anti - government armed forces once attacked the town of Clay on the outskirts of the capital in february this year .
the barracks are located in the town of Dodi , the capital of Monrovia , on the road to neighbouring Cote d &apos;Ivoire and Guinea .
