Bertini reported to the un security council on the same day on the activities and role of this organization , pointing out that the world food program has extended a helping hand to disaster and conflict areas all over the world , saved many lives , and contributed to the reconstruction of some countries , which will help stabilize the situation in conflict areas .
she said that the world food program provided 240 million us dollars of food aid to afghanistan last year , benefiting millions of Afghans .
Bertini appealed to donor countries to donate generously to enable the world food program to complete its new aid mission to afghanistan in 2002 .
he also said that so far , only 70 million us dollars have been raised for the 285 million us dollars project .
Bertini also called on the united nations system and member states to pay attention to the safety of un personnel on humanitarian missions and bring to justice those criminals who harm un personnel .
according to statistics , 204 un personnel have been killed since 1992 , but only 15 criminals have been arrested .
