Xinhua news agency , beijing , april 5 , the german government presented three walls of the Berlin wall , a symbol of the cold war between east and west , to the united nations on the 4 th .
according to foreign reports , each of the three walls is 3.6 meters high and weighs 2.8 tons , and is decorated with an image of a man and a woman embracing each other over a high wall .
the three walls were shipped to new york in october last year to commemorate the reunification of Germany and Germany in 1990 .
owing to the closure of the United Nations garden on the east bank of the New York River since the incident in Tseng 911 , the public was unable to visit it .
UN secretary - general Kofi Annan took the opportunity to say that the end of the east - west division shows that peace is always possible , even in the middle east .
Tilzer , president of the german federal parliament , told Annan that many people had such a wall in their minds before the Berlin wall was built .
the Berlin Wall eventually became history and it was not only the Germans who benefited .
bill Gates fooled on April Fools &apos; Day
Xinhua news agency , beijing , april 5 , bill gates , president of Microsoft corporation , was recently shamed by a Canadian radio station and played a big joke on april fool 's day .
mark Antoine Aoudai and Sebastian Manuel Trudell of Quebec , canada 's CKMF - FM radio station , contacted bill gates by telephone on 1 april , claiming that they were Canadian prime minister Chretien , and had a 10 - minute intimate conversation with him imitating the prime minister 's voice one after another .
topics related to the world economy and the shortcomings of the windows control system , and bill gates was also invited to visit Quebec at an appropriate time .
the radio station played the recording of the conversation in its entertainment program on the evening of the 2 nd and rebroadcast it the next day at the request of the broad masses of listeners .
mark Antoine Odai said afterward that he had not thought it would be so easy to get in touch with bill gates , but his aides had not found and had not thought it would be just an april fool 's day banter .
after learning the truth of the matter , a Microsoft company spokesman said that the radio station had forged some documents to convince Microsoft company that they were Canadian government workers , and warned that although the banter was fun , it was a little too big .
it has been learned that in the past , the radio station used to make fun of some other celebrities such as Celine song - Dion on april fool 's day .
