Xinhua news agency , washington , april 8 , us white house spokesman Fleischer issued a statement on the evening of the 8th , saying that Israel 's withdrawal from Tulkarem and Qalqiliya in the west bank of the Jordan river was only the beginning of a retreat , and relevant parties in the middle east should fulfill their responsibilities .
" this is a start , " Fleischer said in a brief written statement .
just as president bush said on 4 april , all parties in the middle east should fulfill their responsibilities , and the president hopes that all parties will step up their efforts .
Israeli troops began withdrawing from Tulkarem and Qalqiliya in the early hours of the 9th local time . Israel has not yet disclosed when it will completely withdraw its troops from other cities in the west bank .
in a statement to reporters in Tennessee on the same day , bush reiterated that Israel must immediately withdraw its troops from palestinian territory and stressed that his words count as his words .
Bush said that he had already told Israeli prime minister Sharon about the us demand , and that he was waiting for Israel to immediately withdraw its troops .
