Xinhua news agency , beijing , april 13 , foreign ministry spokeswoman Zhang Qiyue confirmed here today that a chinese worker was killed , two other chinese workers were injured , and a chinese worker was missing in an explosion at the jerusalem bus station on the afternoon of april 12 .
Zhang Qiyue said : at around 0400 on 12 april , a suicide bombing occurred at a bus station in central jerusalem , killing six people and injuring more than 70 others on the spot .
in the explosion , one chinese worker was killed , two chinese workers were injured , and another chinese worker was missing .
she said : after the incident occurred , the chinese embassy in Israel attached great importance to it and immediately sent personnel and representatives of relevant companies to jerusalem on the same day to identify the victims , visit the injured , understand the situation , and liaise with relevant parties to deal with the aftermath .
the embassy informed chinese citizens and chinese companies in Israel the same night to pay attention to safety and be cautious in going out .
she said : the chinese government expresses condolences over the deaths of the chinese citizens concerned in the bombing incident and expresses sympathy to their families .
the chinese side condemns the violent activities against innocent civilians and strongly calls on both Israel and palestine to take concrete actions to stop violent confrontation and quell the situation as soon as possible so as to avoid causing more casualties among innocent civilians .
Zhang Qiyue said : the chinese government once again reminds chinese citizens and personnel planning to go to Israel to pay attention to safety , be cautious in travelling , and contact more family members at home . in case of an emergency , please contact the chinese embassy in Israel in a timely manner .
