according to a Syrian news agency report , president Bashar said during the talks : " what happened in palestine has brought the ( middle east ) peace process to a dead end . if we fail to recognize this point , the development of the matter may reach an irretrievable level . at that time , we can only wait for the time of a generation . "
he pointed out that the peace process can only be discussed after Israel withdraws its troops from the palestinian territories it occupies and stops the massacre of Palestinians .
he said : only when both sides are willing to realize peace can peace be realized .
he called on the united states to have a clear view on middle east peace and to play a role in this regard so that the relevant un resolutions can be effectively implemented .
on the issue of palestinian suicide operations , Bashar said that these operations are not the root cause of the current incidents in the occupied palestinian territories , but rather their consequences , and are a counterattack to Israeli practices .
he pointed out that the best way is to eliminate the root causes of tension in the palestinian situation .
according to diplomatic sources , during their talks , Powell and Bashar also discussed the situation along the border between Lebanon and Israel .
Powell arrived in Damascus from Beirut at noon on the same day for a short visit to Syria .
