Xinhua news agency , jerusalem , april 16 ( reporter Zhong cuihua ) - visiting us secretary of state Colin Powell will hold talks with Israeli prime minister Sharon on the afternoon of the 16th and president Arafat of the palestinian national authority on the morning of the 17th respectively .
