Xinhua news agency , Moscow , april 18 , russian president Putin pointed out in his state of the union speech delivered at the joint session of the two houses of the russian parliament on the 18th that russia should become an economically strong and competitive country , should strive to develop constructive normal relations with other countries in the world , and should become a true member of the international community .
