Hebei province enterprises of all kinds actively apply for foreign trade operation rights
Xinhua news agency , Shijiazhuang , april 20 ( reporter : Rao yajie ) - the reporter learned from the Hebei provincial department of foreign trade and economic cooperation that since the beginning of this year , nearly 20,000 enterprises of all kinds in this province have registered with the provincial department of foreign trade and economic cooperation or obtained the approval of the ministry of foreign trade and economic cooperation , 2.3 times as many as in the same period last year .
according to sources , 39 foreign trade companies of all kinds have registered this time , and 17 of them are private foreign trade companies .
there are also dozens of commercial , material , supply and marketing cooperative enterprises and state - owned collective enterprises .
seventy-seven private production enterprises have also applied for the right to operate foreign trade .
the participation of more and more private enterprises is a new phenomenon in the current declaration of foreign trade operation rights .
in july last year , the ministry of foreign trade and economic cooperation further relaxed the conditions and criteria for various types of enterprises to operate their own import and export business , changing from the original examination and approval system to an examination and approval and registration system , stipulating the implementation of unified standards and management methods for enterprises of all types of ownership , thus promoting the enthusiasm of enterprises of all types in filing applications .
