US senator : smallpox terrorists can spread virus at airport
( Washington , usa ) us senator Dr. Frist warned at a hearing on biochemical weapons the day before yesterday that terrorists infected with smallpox could spread the virus throughout the country by spreading deadly viruses or germs at airports and could cause tens of thousands or even millions of deaths .
Frist said at the hearing that when a terrorist infected with smallpox enters an airport , he may transmit the virus to 10 innocent passengers by coughing , sneezing , or even just breathing . the 10 passengers may then spread the virus throughout the country and may cause tens of thousands or even millions of deaths from the disease .
he said that this may be the possible form of weapons of mass destruction .
it does not need to be launched through missiles , nor does it need to be as conspicuous as anthrax .
the infected victims and the defense personnel preventing the attack of this weapon may never know where the virus ( bacteria ) came from .
experts told the senate foreign relations committee : this is part of the reason why biological and chemical weapons are so dangerous .
Biden , chairman of the senate foreign relations committee , said that preventing attacks with biological and chemical weapons is an extremely urgent issue requiring attention .
Helms , the most senior republican member of the committee , said that in order to prevent enemy missiles from attacking the united states with any kind of warhead , the united states still needs to build a missile defense system .
hundreds of thousands of us and south Korean soldiers hold large - scale exercises
( Agence france - presse , Seoul ) - hundreds of thousands of us and south Korean soldiers will conduct the largest - ever military exercise simulating a conflict with north korea on Thursday , drawing criticism from Pyongyang for being a provocative act of war .
US military officers said on the eve of a week - long military exercise that the exercise was purely defensive in nature , but that it took place after the Seoul authorities warned against ignoring the danger of the Korean issue .
this is the largest military exercise since the 1950 - 53 Korean war . since there is no formal treaty to end the conflict on the Korean peninsula , it has become the world 's last cold war front , with nearly two million troops confronting each other on the border .
the us - ROK joint forces command in Seoul said that the exercise from 21 to 27 march will be the first to test its effectiveness by combining two different joint military exercises .
this means that hundreds of thousands of soldiers will participate , but the military did not disclose details .
a spokesman for the joint forces command said that the exercise will mobilize almost every us military unit and ROK military unit on the Korean peninsula , as well as foreign us troops .
37,000 us troops are permanently stationed in the ROK to prevent an attack by the DPRK , which has 1.1 million troops .
South korea also has 650,000 troops .
the joint forces command called the exercise RS0I / FE02 , which is a combination of computerized military exercises and the annual shadowing exercise .
in the past few years , the RSOI exercise alone mobilized 500,000 south Korean troops and 30,000 us troops ( including 20,000 foreign us troops ) .
North Korea accused the United States of staging joint military exercises to provoke a war .
the official Nodong Shimbun even called the us - ROK military exercise a tanga declaration of war .
