( Hong kong ) chinese police recently launched an internal review of the incident of 25 north Koreans breaking into the spanish embassy last week .
it is estimated that in beijing alone , more than 150 Koreans have waited for the opportunity to go to the ROK . the authorities have stepped up security in the embassy area of the ROK , japan , and major embassies of western countries to prevent another incident of trespassing on the embassy building .
