it has been revealed that there are about 10,000 Koreans living in Dongcheng district of beijing and Liangmahe district of Chaoyang district . among them , there are Koreans from northeast china , and there are also people from the DPRK and the ROK respectively . they mainly engage in Korean - style restaurants and bars . since they are all Koreans , they get along well with each other no matter where they come from .
in the past , since there were not many Koreans in beijing , nor were there as many criminal cases involving Xinjiang and Henan nationals , the authorities did not regard them as key targets of surveillance .
according to the report , after the march 14 incident , the public security department first invited the german doctor who assisted the 25 north Koreans to come to the public security department to talk to him , and then sent him to the airport to ask him to leave the country immediately .
