( Pyongyang , Seoul synthesis ) the sandstorm that just swept through northern china violently hit the Korean peninsula yesterday . most regions , including Pyongyang , the capital of the DPRK , and Seoul , the capital of the ROK , were shrouded in brown and yellow dust .
