six routes grounded .
in addition , according to a report by the beijing people 's network , a large sandstorm occurred in south korea yesterday . in addition to the Incheon international airport , six domestic air routes were grounded .
sandstorm sets in across south korea .
according to tests conducted by the ministry of environment of south korea , the amount of fine dust in the sky in Seoul before noon yesterday was 17 times higher than usual , reaching 1,000 micrograms per cubic meter , the highest in history .
affected by the dusty weather across the country , in addition to the normal operation of the Incheon international airport , the ROK has suspended flights on six domestic routes , including Daegu , Weishan , and Pohang , and passengers of more than 30 flights have switched to other means of transportation .
